1. Weakened community capacities to prevent, manage and peacefully resolve disputes; 
2. 52 Local Peace Committees in place with UNDP support. They however require strengthening
3. Over 30.000 community peace facilitators have been equipped with requisite skills. There is need to groom and mentor Community Mediators to support mediation and reconciliation efforts
